OL,3,CParents of 26-year-old Formula One
OL,4,Cengineer raise #40k for cardiac
OL,5,Cscreening
OL,7,FThe parents of a Formula One engineer
OL,8,Fwho died of a cardiac arrest have
OL,9,Fraised over #40,000 for more heart
OL,10,Fscreenings in young people.
OL,12,FAnthony Lane was working for Lewis
OL,13,FHamilton's Mercedes team when he
OL,14,Fsuddenly collapsed while using his
OL,15,Fexercise bike at home.
OL,17,FHis parents, with the help of Mercedes
OL,18,Fand the Rotary club of Wylde Green,
OL,19,Fhave raised significant funds for more
OL,20,Fcardiac screenings in the area.
