OL,7,FA keen engineer from a young age,
OL,8,FAnthony saved up all of his pocket
OL,9,Fmoney and brought his first car, a
OL,10,Fmini, when he was just 14.
OL,12,FFrom then on, he went to the and was a
OL,13,Ftechnical director of the racing team,
OL,14,Fbefore he landed his dream job at
OL,15,FMercedes.
