OL,7,FSpeaking on Mercedes, his parents
OL,8,Fsaid: "Everything at Mercedes is very
OL,9,Fconfidential because obviously, you
OL,10,Fknow, everybody's tried to develop
OL,11,Fthat car, so it's better than somebody
OL,12,Felse's car."
OL,14,F"So he really didn't tell us a lot
OL,15,Fabout it. All he said was he was Mr.
OL,16,FCrankshaft. So that was his speciality
OL,17,Fin the engine".
