OL,7,FOn their son they say that Anthony was
OL,8,Fa "perfectionist", who even when he
OL,9,Fspent his spare time making pizzas
OL,10,Fwould make the "most perfect pizza
OL,11,Fdough".
OL,13,FHis father Paul said: "It had to be
OL,14,Fperfect, which is aligned with the
OL,15,FMercedes, you know, everything very
OL,16,Fprecise, very high tolerances."
OL,18,FHis parents say that Anthony was
OL,19,F"sporty and active" and had no signs
OL,20,Fof obvious health problems.
