OL,7,FBut out of the blue, his mother
OL,8,Freceived a call to say Anthony's
OL,9,Fgirlfriend had found him collapsed on
OL,10,Fthe floor.
OL,12,FAt aged just 26, he had a cardiac
OL,13,Farrest.
OL,15,FHis mother Penny added: "It happened
OL,16,Fincredibly quickly. He just got off
OL,17,Fhis bike and just fallen onto the
OL,18,Fground. West Midlands Ambulance
OL,19,FService had arrived and the air
OL,20,Fambulance was there with the doctors.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
