OL,7,F"They were fantastic. And I then had
OL,8,Fthis conversation on video call with
OL,9,Fthe air ambulance doctor who said:
OL,10,F'yes, they've done everything they
OL,11,Fcould.' But it was it was too late.
OL,12,FAnthony was long gone."
OL,14,FAfter his death, his name was
OL,15,Fdisplayed on the nose cone of both
OL,16,FLouis Hamilton and George Russell's
OL,17,Fcars during the Mexico Grand Prix in
OL,18,F2022.
