OL,7,FEvery week in the UK, 12 apparently
OL,8,Ffit and healthy young people under 35,
OL,9,Flike Anthony, die of an undiagnosed
OL,10,Fheart condition.
OL,12,FThe CEO of Charity Cardiac risk in the
OL,13,FYoung (CRY) says the majority of
OL,14,Fdeaths can be prevented by cardiac
OL,15,Fscreening. The charity is also
OL,16,Fcampaigning for a national testing
OL,17,Fprogram.
